{"tid":1910772,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愈大愈自閉 都唔知真正既自己係點","createTime":"2020-03-05T02:01:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T06:44:14.000Z","uid":70362,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"51e882cb890edd1f803eb76fc984de6dc209c968","tid":1910772,"uid":70362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"曾經我都係一個幾social既人<br />\n中學可以同時存在係幾個圈子 <br />\n都算係風頭躉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到u 經歷過一唔開心既事 全部要獨自面對（冇兄弟姊妹）<br />\n慢慢自己好似已經唔想同人溝通 覺得都唔會有人明白我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加出黎做左幾年野<br />\n同同事工作上溝通 9吹下個d完全冇問題既<br />\n但已經去到咩都唔會主動share<br />\n放假除左屋企人 可以一句野都唔同人講（以前住hall試過幾日冇講過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知我本質係中學咁yo定依加既我先係真正既我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一方面又好想好似以前咁開心<br />\n另一方面又好想依加咁自由<br />\n好似自我知出現嚴重問題咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a530adce7e3f028e8d629a5adbbfa0b2fe8081","tid":1910772,"uid":288731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:14:35.000Z","msg":"搵返啲中同囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，老友鬼鬼傾返電話，人會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d072a102d12affad1df4b28583b70510c777c86","tid":1910772,"uid":175783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:18:42.000Z","msg":"可以同你做朋友傾心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b71c0ecca8bd376082738f0642039f2b1be5f3","tid":1910772,"uid":71637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi